e gets injured while you\'re shooting on location. Instead of suing you, they ask you to pay $5,000 for medical expenses. We\'ll cover it.</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"uk-text-center uk-text-small\">This is a brief summary of your policy and does not supersede the policy documents. If you want full details, please call us.</div>'),(37605,676,'_crb_block_layouts_accordion-_crb_class_3',''),(37606,676,'_crb_block_layouts_accordion-_crb_title_3','Got questions? We’ve got answers'),(37607,676,'_crb_block_layouts_accordion-_crb_accordion_item_3_-_crb_accordion_title_0','How do I get a Certificate of Insurance?'),(37608,676,'_crb_block_layouts_accordion-_crb_accordion_item_3_-_crb_coverage_content_0','We give you unlimited certificates of insurance, free of charge. Once you\'ve purchased a policy, <a href=\"https://track.next-insurance.com/links?serial=65551&channel=ps&source=product&campaign=get-coi&adgroup=photographer&position=lp-faq\" target=\"_blank\">Click Here</a> to input the details of your venue or client. We\'ll get you your certificate as soon as your policy is ready, within one business day.'),(37609,676,'_crb_block_layouts_accordion-_crb_accordion_item_3_-_crb_accordion_title_1','Do I have to pay the entire premium now?'),(37610,676,'_crb_block_layouts_accordion-_crb_accordion_item_3_-_crb_coverage_content_1','No, to make it easier on your budget we allow you to make monthly payments.'),(37611,676,'_crb_block_layouts_accordion-_crb_accordion_item_3_-_crb_accordion_title_2','How do I report a claim?'),(37612,676,'_crb_block_layouts_accordion-_crb_accordion_item_3_-_crb_coverage_content_2','Easy. Just contact us at support@next-insurance.com or call (855) 222-5919 to report a claim. We\'ll be happy to help you with the claims process and get you back on track.'),(37613,676,'_crb_block_layouts_accordion-_crb_accordion_item_3_-_crb_accordion_title_3','Who is Next Insurance?'),(37614,676,'_crb_block_layouts_accordion-_crb_accordion_item_3_-_crb_c