siness owners, and the negative relationship between policy holders and policy providers can finally be re-imagined.\r\n\r\nBut changing the face of insurance for small businesses is not a one and done situation. Yes, we\'re giving our users better policies at better prices. Yes, we\'re providing them with more transparency than ever before. And yes, we\'re doing so with a dramatically simplified and expedited sign-up process.\r\n\r\nSomething to be proud of? Definitely. Something that motivated us to push even further? Absolutely.\r\n\r\nToday, you don\'t even need to peruse around our website, all you need to do is message our chatbot and within minutes you\'ll be signed up to the most comprehensive insurance policy ever offered for personal trainers. Try it <a href=\"https://www.messenger.com/t/Personal.Trainer.Insurance\">Here</a>\r\n\r\nThe way we see it, it\'s time that insurance started working for you and the first step is meeting you where you are.','The First Ever Chatbot For Small Business Insurance: Because who said insurance can’t be easy?','','publish','closed','open','','first-ever-chatbot-small-business-insurance-said-insurance-cant-easy','','','2017-03-29 07:18:37','2017-03-29 14:18:37','',0,'http://www.next-insurance.com/?p=1136',0,'post','',0),(1138,3,'2017-03-14 04:36:19','2017-03-14 11:36:19','','The Future of Social Network','Human and robots to work together in the near future. This combination will accelerate developing technology. Businessman and cyborg organizes social media.','inherit','open','closed','','the-future-of-social-network','','','2017-03-14 04:39:10','2017-03-14 11:39:10','',1136,'http://www.next-insurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/iStock-496800562.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1140,3,'2017-03-15 01:56:10','2017-03-15 08:56:10','Today, we\'re very excited to announce the launch of the world\'s first full insurance sign up via Facebook Messenger. Alongside our friends at SmallTalk, we\'ve built the first fully functi