ce and service, in a way that works best for you and allows you to spend more time nourishing your business. We are here to help you succeed.','Do-it-Yourself: Proof Of Insurance','','publish','closed','open','','do-it-yourself-proof-of-insurance','','','2017-05-01 07:05:01','2017-05-01 14:05:01','',0,'http://www.next-insurance.com/?p=1339',0,'post','',0),(1340,3,'2017-05-01 04:12:21','2017-05-01 11:12:21','','About Us','','trash','closed','closed','','__trashed','','','2017-05-01 04:12:40','2017-05-01 11:12:40','',0,'http://www.next-insurance.com/?page_id=1340',0,'page','',0),(1341,3,'2017-05-01 04:15:15','2017-05-01 11:15:15','','AboutUs_Hero','','inherit','closed','closed','','aboutus_hero','','','2017-05-01 04:15:15','2017-05-01 11:15:15','',650,'http://www.next-insurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/AboutUs_Hero.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1342,3,'2017-05-01 04:17:23','2017-05-01 11:17:23','','HowWorks_1','','inherit','closed','closed','','howworks_1','','','2017-05-01 04:17:23','2017-05-01 11:17:23','',650,'http://www.next-insurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/HowWorks_1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1343,3,'2017-05-01 04:17:51','2017-05-01 11:17:51','','HowWorks_2','','inherit','closed','closed','','howworks_2','','','2017-05-01 04:17:51','2017-05-01 11:17:51','',650,'http://www.next-insurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/HowWorks_2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1344,3,'2017-05-01 04:18:11','2017-05-01 11:18:11','','HowWorks_3','','inherit','closed','closed','','howworks_3','','','2017-05-01 04:18:11','2017-05-01 11:18:11','',650,'http://www.next-insurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/HowWorks_3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1345,3,'2017-05-01 04:32:15','2017-05-01 11:32:15','','Guy','','inherit','closed','closed','','guy','','','2017-05-01 04:32:15','2017-05-01 11:32:15','',650,'http://www.next-insurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Guy.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1346,3,'2017-05-01 04:34:27','2017-05-01 11:3